title: [Vornavis, West Road]
description: Thousands of sunflowers decorate the fields south of the road here, painting the landscape yellow in the moonlight.  Tall grasses grow through the sunflowers, and the leaves rustle against the dry grasses in the breeze.

Thousands of sunflowers decorate the fields south of the road here, painting the landscape a vibrant yellow.  Tall grasses grow through the sunflowers, and the leaves rustle against the dry grasses in the breeze.  Bees swarm about the field busily.
